              .card(data-aos="fade-up")
                .card-header
                  %a.collapsed.card-link{"data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseOne"}
                    %span.icon
                    What is the Tokenmom?
                #collapseOne.collapse{"data-parent" => "#accordion"}
                  .card-body
                    TokenMom is the Korean's First Futuristic Real Decentralized Exchange
              .card(data-aos="fade-up")
                .card-header
                  %a.collapsed.card-link{"data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseTwo"}
                    %span.icon
                    How can I purchase TM token?
                #collapseTwo.collapse{"data-parent" => "#accordion"}
                  .card-body
                    Tokenmom does not proceed with ICO etc, which can only be purchased on Tokenmom Exchange.
              .card(data-aos="fade-up")
                .card-header
                  %a.collapsed.card-link{"data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseThree"}
                    %span.icon
                    How much is the trade fee?
                #collapseThree.collapse{"data-parent" => "#accordion"}
                  .card-body
                    Free trading fee for 2 months, After 2 months, the highest fee shall be 0.05% or less

